image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-9207ae35-a86d-437b-b9e2-64baa4112c99\", \"src\" : \"https://copingwithmsa.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/what-is-autonomic-dysfunction.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"600\", \"originalHeight\" : \"600\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"0\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://copingwithmsa.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/what-is-autonomic-dysfunction.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-9207ae35-a86d-437b-b9e2-64baa4112c99\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\", \"fileSize\": \"0\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bcffb6d7-449b-4f81-9231-231a77cf214c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-7e0b55b7-f1db-443a-a303-f52cacba12c2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs28 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d62dbd25-1a82-422a-b170-ee88f538df07\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-8e46d123-d4bd-49a7-b159-3353084730c1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs28 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-400b6f77-dbec-44ea-b5bf-73de37dbd113\"><b>5. 국내 현황</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-23997295-487e-4af0-b891-ce78faeb5377\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-652f9cb0-91fd-4127-9bd2-d3650eb247b0\">건강보험심사평가원 통계에 따르면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-47a960e7-9194-4073-9cd3-ba91053faf27\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-90abf339-4844-412f-b1bd-a43d3a9e77a1\">2011년 약 12,468명 → 2021년 27,749명으로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-b271e4d3-8e5f-438a-9d56-64a46bdebbcf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7a028486-8a6a-4fb0-a42c-5e70a65a1d36\">10년간 약 120% 증가!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-5e7d4d30-8c26-40cd-b2b6-88d97d144c88\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6ddde652-8550-47cd-bfa4-dc6a745cfff2\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-63a6aee6-6e31-4b40-9e48-74bdaee8d777\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7a391b54-33ef-4f31-8944-c0964bf3435f\">이는 스트레스 증가, 디지털 기기 과사용, 수면 불규칙, 만성질환 증가와 관련이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-b37c6e45-0505-467f-bb1d-ff529ae51bd3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8a1c3b8a-c63f-4e70-8e1d-d62221c2fe01\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-1e32aa14-eed3-49c5-88e9-dd2be7b74593\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-67b4fa73-f6c1-4adb-8f20-1855fe7feee6\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-3e9f9be9-6ce2-4d8b-8f70-e9464588b7b7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs28 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-19587685-ad1d-4e23-b6c8-412a3f9fbf56\"><b>6. 관리 및 치료 방향</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-eb87b3a0-e3b9-4bab-b1b4-a69ea07b2125\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-acb273b0-21b3-4779-9ad5-ebbbeca7f289\">- 생활습관 교정</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-b7dd9364-850d-496e-81e2-91532d7be296\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-099102ce-77b4-4dd2-8982-2f7a3d682d2a\">- 규칙적 수면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-2bd6b9de-88d2-4147-a849-4a54be058cf9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aba0c21b-97b6-47c9-a789-a9489d3b2926\">- 스트레스 관리</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-7860e52b-8dd0-4411-9a08-ee175841a8b1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-accd8c97-1c3c-4530-a45c-8168f4d4c3d9\">- 적절한 운동</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-54dfbebd-415d-4cfd-9f7e-f4ff00badad8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2338ba0d-b7b0-4762-a0c8-1a7b5e9a534a\">- 영양 관리</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-77979679-be2d-4c35-9709-5123700210e0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c70bb4e1-f88f-4f2f-b99b-faafa7f9c3ba\">- 필요 시 전문적 자율신경 평가 및 치료</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-75de9d9e-4559-4ab8-b2df-8a3f4680c960\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d549e114-581d-4324-8010-ab12f7274d0e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-bcffb6d7-449b-4f81-9231-231a77cf214c\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d84b9b40-7018-460c-8c6e-6397ce4d4a27\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:275px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d84b9b40-7018-460c-8c6e-6397ce4d4a27\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/04f612ac9e7ec4a4.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"275\", \"originalHeight\" : \"183\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"5674\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/04f612ac9e7ec4a4.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/04f612ac9e7ec4a4.jpg\" data-width=\"275\" data-height=\"183\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-d84b9b40-7018-460c-8c6e-6397ce4d4a27\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\", \"fileSize\": \"5674\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7a73d87a-ca69-43f4-b072-fa03c93b3027\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-cad3bf10-986e-404c-9804-7272d3df2611\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ee9e032e-b077-4a75-ab28-80f14454239a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-4b7f31c8-3079-4ca0-83d4-2f662c313e80\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5b6e8895-acc0-49e4-abb5-bcadba98d7b9\">드러난 신체증상만을 치료하기보다 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-8cb11073-0f7b-40a5-9a54-17416b0a0e81\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6e3c0af9-9262-4ff6-98bf-705199bcf4e7\">자율신경계의 교감신경 부교감신경 사이의 균형 회복을 목표로 하는 통합적 시각의 치료접근이 필요합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-faf3652f-2756-4d6c-aefd-99a6dabc795b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dd3630ae-8ce2-4aa0-9f37-af2c1969dd0b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-636a4e3b-b70b-48bd-aea5-ab0e1a5f4e97\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3d2b4e9b-7495-4ab9-a11d-8914c5a0f4ad\">자율신경 실조증은 이전부터 한의원에서 많이 치료하던 질환입니다. 닥터쇼핑을 해도 치료가 되지 않는 분들, &#x27;신경성이다&#x27;라는 진단에 딱히 치료할 방법이 없던 분들, 본인은 괴로운데 주변에서는 꾀병이라 여겨서 마음이 힘든 분들이 한의원에서 치료 받고 다시 건강을 되찾는 경우가 많죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-f3afa7f6-77cf-4b14-8789-424ac19d590d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-67050155-2aa4-417e-ab0b-ffbd2c3e121b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-b12c6c02-f0c0-404b-ac84-13234e92e0a6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-edac79b1-9e4e-4251-89fc-376cf87beffa\">자율신경 증상을 겪고 있다면 한의원에서 진료를 받아보세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-6a872242-2710-4211-8d3e-657b2b829824\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fbbb9e4e-7c03-4824-84cc-7ca671dbbef7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-c7025cde-e0f5-4ecc-89d4-e0e3ce1c9fc9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a85a0a85-bf33-4b33-aeca-5a7c76fc380b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-7a73d87a-ca69-43f4-b072-fa03c93b3027\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-oglink se-l-large_image\" id=\"SE-dabe2e8a-260c-4bbd-bb97-8ff6e996bd06\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-oglink se-l-large_image se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-oglink\">\n    